    narr:Actor_DesignCollaborator skos:note "Former designer and creative director at Vouch; close friend and informal advisor to aswritten.ai; currently working on a collaborator with Tony Maley and a technical collaborator. On the June 29 2026 call, provided brand-strategy counsel: the founder's personal vision should function as a distinct authority layer that cyclically builds credibility for both the person and the business. Recipient of Scarlet's original introductory email, which he still cites as the best introductory email he has ever read and which he argues matters more now than it did then. Contributed the 'amplification' framing on the June 29 2026 call." .
  }
}
